# Final Security Code-Review — NL2SQL Generator
**Pass date:** 2026-04-25 | **Scope:** All backend (Node/Express) + AI-service (FastAPI/Python) files

---

## ✅ Summary — No HIGH Findings Remain

Every HIGH finding from the earlier checklist has been resolved.
Two **MEDIUM** and two **LOW/INFO** observations are documented below for completeness.

---

## 🟢 HIGH — ALL CLEAR

| Area | Check | Status |
|---|---|---|
| **Auth — JWT** | Secret validated at startup (≥16 chars, ≥3 char classes, no placeholder) | ✅ PASS |
| **Auth — token read** | `requireAuth` reads cookie **and** Bearer; both verified via `jwt.verify` | ✅ PASS |
| **Auth — error exposure** | Invalid/expired token returns generic `"Invalid or expired token"` only | ✅ PASS |
| **Service-to-service** | `secrets.compare_digest` used for timing-safe token comparison | ✅ PASS |
| **Token bootstrap** | Both `JWT_SECRET` and `AI_SERVICE_TOKEN` refuse weak/placeholder values at process start | ✅ PASS |
| **Input validation (Express)** | `express-validator` used on every mutating route; validation errors returned before any DB call | ✅ PASS |
| **Input validation (FastAPI)** | Pydantic `Field(min_length, max_length)` enforced on `user_query`, `schema_context`, `dialect` | ✅ PASS |
| **Dialect allow-list** | Express + Mongoose both constrain dialect to 5 known values | ✅ PASS |
| **Ownership checks** | Every DB query scopes to `userId: req.user.id`; no unscoped lookups | ✅ PASS |
| **Schema PATCH mass-assignment** | `{ ...req.body }` in `findOneAndUpdate` is bounded by the mongoose schema (strictQuery: true) | ✅ PASS |
| **SQL read-only enforcement** | `_enforce_read_only` in `sql_generator.py` rejects any LLM output not starting with `SELECT`/`WITH` | ✅ PASS |
| **Password hashing** | bcrypt with cost-factor 10; plain text never stored | ✅ PASS |
| **HttpOnly cookie** | `httpOnly: true`, `sameSite: 'lax'`, `secure` in production | ✅ PASS |
| **CORS** | Both services lock `allow_origins` / `origin` to env-configured frontend URL only | ✅ PASS |
| **Rate limiting** | Auth: 20 req/15 min · Query (Express): 45 req/60 s · Query (FastAPI): 60 req/60 s | ✅ PASS |
| **Error handler** | 5xx errors return generic message; `err.message` only surfaced for 4xx | ✅ PASS |
| **Secrets in git** | All `.env` files gitignored at root + service level; `.env.example` uses placeholder values | ✅ PASS |
| **`console.error` on 5xx** | Logs full error server-side only — not sent to client | ✅ PASS |

